{"tid":1616733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈，今日開始再無“和理非”","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:12:12.000Z","uid":56518,"like":171,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9db047458347297e100256eca68a8645e02a5296","tid":1616733,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"from fb 作者<br />\n阻你一分鐘，思考一下<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n而在抗爭運動上，本來大家的身份都只是「人民」，人民係可以起義改變社會的，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只是你被指派一個「和理非」的身份，將你變成一個家屬，令抗爭運動的自由地帶，劃分為手術室內和室外。這歹毒的定義，將無數的你困住了，你們對抗爭感到不得其門而入，就是這個原因。一道無形的房門，在街頭隔絕了兩幫人。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這一代的朋友，請你們清楚意識到「身份政治」的卑鄙和可畏，現代人要自由，首要成為一個「無身份的人」。//<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你無深刻反省過這個問題，香港何談甚麼未來？<br />\n<br />\n人只會繼續白白地被拘捕，白白地死去。</span></strong>//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家，唔好再作繭自縛</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">You are all, you are everything</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"29529c3f2f03e82c3c0e91fee9b1ef92cbc576f3","tid":1616733,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ce4a1952d9d22249fb2d0b90eeaf34297b0efca","tid":1616733,"uid":257737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"You are all, you are everything！"},{"pid":"b6e9f41f8c094f6d6bb900f05cc69bbb51942519","tid":1616733,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45524484c5ccccafbdf75c95f8c41ea430111c50","tid":1616733,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0e41a0746c5a3fb5025f0bed2fd16bf35ac2027","tid":1616733,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:59:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6038eb5e72841198854f6182138e64695bc83a20","tid":1616733,"uid":56518,"like":0,"di